Matanedi ledu bashanedi ledu…
Choopu basha naku chalule…
Ninnanedi ledu repanedi ledu…
Neti roju naku chalule…
Na annade ledu…nenannade ledu…
Nalona virithota virabusene…
Ye katthi pidi ledu…
Ye raktha thadi ledu…
Nuni metthani prema nanu gelichene…
Kalisi poye manasu…
Tholisari nilichipoye adugu
Ninu cheri nilichipoye manasu
Prathi sari kalisi veyi adugu
Paruvama…

O where would I be
Without this joy inside of me
It makes me want to come alive
It makes me want to fly into the sky
O where would I be…
If I didn’t have you next to me
O where would I be
O where…o where…

